Gunmen suspected to be kidnappers have invaded the staff quarters of Ahmadu Bello University, Zaria, Kaduna State, kidnapping a lecturer identified as Dr Bako. Bako was abducted along with his wife and daughter.  The incident took place on Monday around 12:50am at Sardauna Crescent, Area BZ, ABU Main Campus, Samaria, Zaria. The institution’s spokesperson, Malam Auwalu Umar, confirmed the incident in a statement. The incident comes barely a week after three persons were kidnapped at the Nuhu Bamalli Polytechnic also in  Zaria. See Also






